  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git分支合并的示意图，用来演示多分支交叉合并的场景。主分支叫branch_m，左右各有一个辅助分支branch_l和branch_n，要能清楚显示它们的合并顺序。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_m",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_n"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个分支。branch_m作为主分支放在中间，branch_l在左边order 0，branch_n在右边order 2。初始提交a之后，两个辅助分支同时切出来对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_m",
        "branch_l",
        "branch_n",
        "commit a"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个结构。然后branch_n先提交一个u，branch_l提交一个f。接着branch_m要先后合并branch_n和branch_l，形成一个双向合并的基础。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit u",
        "commit f",
        "merge branch_n",
        "merge branch_l"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把这部分画出来。branch_m合并完两个分支后，接下来是让两个辅助分支再反向合并branch_m？这样形成循环依赖的演示效果？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_n merge branch_m",
        "branch_l merge branch_m"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，正是要展示这种循环合并。branch_n和branch_l各自merge branch_m之后，branch_m还要再merge它们一次，最后两个辅助分支各自再提交一个新节点w和h收尾。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_m merge branch_n",
        "branch_m merge branch_l",
        "commit w",
        "commit h"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构完成了。我检查一下显示设置，分支线和提交标签都要显示出来，调试级别用debug方便排查问题。整体效果应该能清晰展示三次双向合并的完整流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "debug"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，最后两个提交的位置确认一下——w是在branch_n上，h是在branch_l上，对吧？别放反了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit w",
        "commit h",
        "branch_n",
        "branch_l"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误，w在branch_n末端，h在branch_l末端。整个图从初始提交a开始，经过三轮交叉合并，最终三个分支都保持同步，结构完整。",
